Odaily Planet Daily News According to the official post of GMGN.ai on the X platform, the second trading competition jointly initiated by GMGN and BNB CHAIN ​​is in progress, with a prize pool of 100 BNB, including: 
The first place will receive 25 BNB; 
The second place will receive 18 BNB
The third place will receive 12 BNB; 
The 4th to 50th place will share the remaining 45 BNB. 
The results of the competition will be officially announced at 23:59 on March 26 (Singapore time).
